    "WignerBasisKeys[{n, s}] returns the SU(2) irreducible basis (the total \
angular momentum basis) for the system of n spins of magnitude s in the \
symbolic form. WignerBasisKeys[{n, s} -> t] returns the basis of the SU(2) \
irreducible subspace corresponding to the single total angular momentum t. \
WignerBasisKeys[{s1, s2, ..., s n}] or WignerBasisKeys[{s1, s2, ..., sn} -> \
t] returns the basis for spins {s1, s2, ..., sn}.", "synonyms" -> {}, 
